in washington for treatment which leaves him bedridden 
his doctor jose luis saca told the ap the latest round of 
chemotherapy was particularly devastating duarte is given little 
to no chance of reaching his 64th birthday in november 
duarte considers himself to a great degree personally 
responsible for conditions permitting the unprecedented succession 
