the richmond accounting firm where he worked 
he was charged with fleeing to avoid prosecution he faces five 
counts of firstdegree murder in new jersey for the 1971 shooting 
deaths of his mother wife and three children in westfield 
the fbi said list 63 was identified by his fingerprints he 
was ordered jailed pending a monday bond hearing 
