sides of the office building they said 
the governmentapproved plan for the site south of the thames 
river would cost 158 million more than the initial plan and would 
reduce some office and parking space the developers said 
the remains of the 16th century theater were discovered nearly 
six months ago during demolition to prepare for the office 
building the rose is the only elizabethan theater ever uncovered 
shakespeare is thought to have made his debut as an actor at the 
rose in 1592 and to have acted there in his own play henry vi 
