agriculture department to buy more apples to help sagging sales 
caused by findings that alar a growth enhancer sprayed on some 
apples can cause cancer the measure was sponsored by sens brock 
adams dwash and slade gorton rwash whose home state is one 
of the nations leading apple producers 
