sousuke uno became japans new prime minister 
friday and pledged to make a clean start after months of a 
bribery scandal that shook the establishment and soiled the image 
of the governing liberal democratic party 
parliament approved uno early in the day ending the partys 
fiveweek search for someone unblemished by the scandal in which 
