intervention during a central american summit tentatively scheduled 
for july 
we hope that nicaragua will cut its links with the fmln he 
said 
the armed forces tuesday exhibited nearly 400 sovietdesigned 
ak47 assault rifles 50 sovietmade grenade launchers and piles of 
other munition military spokesmen called it the biggest logistical 
blow to the rebels in years 
but the insurgents on their clandestine radio said it was a 
show staged to implicate nicaragua and ensure continued us 
military aid el salvador receives more than 1 million a day in 
us economic and military assistance 
according to the armys june orders the graduating class of 
colonels known as la tandona consolidated its power retaining 
or gaining command of seven of the eight army brigades the 
colonels are not likely to modify significantly the current 
strategy of low intensity conflict 
the selection of cristianis defense minister deeply divided the 
armed forces last week 
cristiani and other senior arena party officials favored 
hardline air force commander gen rafael bustillo according to 
military and political sources col rene ponce in charge of the 
joint chiefs of staff also aspired to the portfolio 
because their rivalry threatened to split the armed forces 
sources said gen humberto larios was chosen as a compromise 
candidate but he is considered a stopgap 
bustillo who it is thought would escalate the conflict sharply 
if he had charge of defense reportedly is supported by key 
colonels who do not belong to the tandona 
ponce leads the tandona and command changes announced 
friday make it likely he eventually will win the contest for the 
defense ministry which is expected to change hands in about six 
months 
