what sect members say was a ritual designed to provide magical 
protection for their drug smuggling 
authorities uncovered 15 bodies in matamoros at least four of 
them the victims of gruesome ritual murders and they suspect 
constanzo or his mexico city associates of being responsible for a 
series of earlier cult slayings 
