foleys office furnishings reflect his leadership philosophy 
instead of the big imposing desk preferred by most members of 
congress foley has a coffee table surrounded by enough sofas and 
chairs to accommodate at least 18 visitors his belgian shephard 
alice can usually be found lounging on one of the carpets of 
vibrant blues and reds 
another part of foleys design for success comes from a lesson 
he says he learned from saint exuperys the little prince in 
