congress in this decade 
just this year foley was host of the extraordinary talks that 
in midapril produced a budget agreement for the next fiscal year 
and he was pivotal in the bipartisan deal with the bush 
administration over central america policy 
a year earlier he chaired the economic summit sessions that 
followed the october 1987 crash of the stock market prior to that 
he engineered the final agreements on the grammrudman budget law 
