because the government said the civilian labor force fell by 
49000 people to 1236 million that indicated the influx of 
students into the summer labor force generally seen in may or 
june did not occur in any great number last month 
in a positive sign the government said the number of part time 
workers last month who wanted to work full time fell by about 
300000 to 48 million 
